  <brief_title>Evaluate the Glycemic Control of CKD-501 in Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus</brief_title>
  <official_title>To Investigate the Glycemic Control and Lipid Profile of CKD-501 Monotherapy in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus:a Eight-week, Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind, Parallel-Group, Placebo-controlled, Dose-ranging Study.</official_title>
