  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the safety and effectiveness of three doses of CKD-501
      compared to placebo in lowering fasting plasma glucose levels in people with type 2 diabetes
      for 8 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
